<div class="bg-green-800 border-b-4 border-amber-500 py-4 px-6 flex justify-between items-center shadow-md">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-amber-400">MYSIC</h1>
</div>
<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-100">
  <!-- ヒーローセクション -->
  <div class="relative h-[60vh] bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url(/top-background.jpg)">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex items-center justify-center px-4">
      <div class="bg-white/95 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-2xl border-4 border-amber-500 max-w-xl text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-green-800 mb-6">
          自分だけの音楽、<br>世界に一つの<span class="text-amber-500">Mysic</span>。
        </h1>
        <div class="space-x-4">
          <%= link_to "ログイン", new_user_session_path, 
              class: "px-6 py-3 bg-green-800 hover:bg-green-700 text-amber-300 font-semibold rounded shadow-lg transition" %>
          <%= link_to "新規登録", new_user_registration_path, 
              class: "px-6 py-3 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-green-900 font-bold rounded shadow-lg transition" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5つのステップ -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 border-t-4 border-green-800">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-green-800 text-center mb-8 pb-4 border-b-2 border-amber-400">
        クリエイティブを支える5つのステップ
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="p-4 border-l-4 border-green-800 bg-gray-50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800">1. 録音</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">歌声や演奏をその場で録音</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 border-l-4 border-green-800 bg-gray-50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800">2. 伴奏再生</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">YouTubeの伴奏に合わせてパフォーマンス</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 border-l-4 border-green-800 bg-gray-50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800">3. 簡易編集</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">録音を聴き直して調整・保存</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 border-l-4 border-green-800 bg-gray-50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800">4. 仲間とつながる</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">音楽仲間を見つけて交流</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 border-l-4 border-green-800 bg-gray-50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800">5. 投稿サポート</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">YouTubeへの投稿をカンタンに</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <%= link_to "今すぐ始める", new_user_registration_path, 
            class: "inline-block px-10 py-3 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-green-900 font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg transition" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>